---
import Header from "@components/header.astro";
import "@styles/global.module.css";
import Scripts from "@components/scripts.astro";
import Footer from "@components/footer.astro";
import Meta from "@components/meta.astro";
import Cursor from "@components/cursor.astro";
import Tabs from "@components/Tabs.astro";
import Tab from "@components/Tab.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <Meta name="Akabot Privacy Policy" description="This page describes our privacy policy and how we collect and use your data." />
    <Scripts />
    <Cursor />
  </head>

  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <Tabs>
        <Tab href="/project/akabot">About</Tab>
        <Tab href="/project/akabot/privacy" selected>Privacy Policy</Tab>
        <Tab href="/project/akabot/tos">Terms of Service</Tab>
        <Tab href="/project/akabot/changelog">Changelog</Tab>
      </Tabs>
      <p>At Akabot, we take your privacy very seriously. We are committed to protecting your personal information and ensuring that your experience with our Discord bot is secure and confidential.</p>
      <h2>Data Collection</h2>
      <p>Akabot does not collect or store any personal data or information about its users. When you interact with Akabot on Discord, we do not gather, process, or retain any of your private data, messages, or server information.</p>
      <h2>Data Usage</h2>
      <p>Since Akabot does not collect any user data, we do not have any means to use or share your information. Your interactions with the bot are completely private and are not used for any purpose.</p>
      <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>Akabot does not share, sell, or distribute any user data with third parties. As we do not collect any information, there is nothing for us to share.</p>
      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>As Akabot does not store any user data, there is no risk of unauthorized access, data breaches, or security vulnerabilities related to your personal information.</p>
      <h2>Changes to the Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. However, as Akabot's core principle is to not collect any user data, this policy is
        unlikely to undergo significant changes.
      </p>
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions or concerns about Akabot's privacy practices, please feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:akatsuki2555@waifu.club">akatsuki2555@waifu.club</a>.</p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
